---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Blog - Gil Gatson"
  description="Insights on technology, geopolitics, business strategy, and entrepreneurship from Gil Gatson."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    
    <p class="intro">
      Insights on technology, geopolitics, business strategy, and entrepreneurship.
    </p>
    
    <div class="blog-grid">
      <article class="blog-card">
        <h2><a href="/blog/america-losing-ai-race">Why America Is Losing the AI Race to China</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">December 29, 2025</p>
        <p>
          In 2025, the AI contest is not about who drops the flashiest frontier model. It is about who can scale it, power it, staff it, and deploy it. China is winning the compounding game: open-weight distribution, electricity capacity, and coordinated deployment.
        </p>
        <a href="/blog/america-losing-ai-race" class="read-more">Read more ‚Üí</a>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-card">
        <h2><a href="/blog/energy-infrastructure-ai">Energy Infrastructure: The Hidden Constraint on AI Development</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">Coming Soon</p>
        <p>
          Why data centers need massive amounts of electricity, and how America's energy infrastructure compares to China's nuclear reactor buildout.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-card">
        <h2><a href="/blog/open-source-trap">The Open Source Trap: How America Is Helping Its Rivals</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">Coming Soon</p>
        <p>
          The unintended consequences of open-source AI development from a national security perspective.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
    
    <div class="coming-soon">
      <p>üìù Blog posts coming soon. Check back for regular updates on AI, geopolitics, and business strategy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--color-gray);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    
    .blog-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    
    .blog-card {
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    
    .blog-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .blog-card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .blog-card h2 a {
      color: var(--color-text);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .blog-card h2 a:hover {
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }
    
    .meta {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--color-gray);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .read-more {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .read-more:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .coming-soon {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: var(--color-gray);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
